---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout locale="en" title="1st Choice CE">
  <section class="project-hero"><div class="hero-bg" style="background-image:url('/projects/firstchoice/1ST-CHOICE-2048x1177.jpg')"></div><div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="container"><div class="hero-content"><a href="/#results" class="back-link"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M15 5L5 10L15 15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>Back</a><h1 class="project-title">1st Choice CE</h1><p class="project-tagline">Identity system for online education</p><p class="project-context">Education / Online — USA</p></div></div>
  </section>
  <section class="project-section"><div class="container"><span class="section-label-text"><i>01</i> Problem</span><p class="project-body">They had quality courses but their visual presence didn't communicate professionalism. Students dropped off before enrolling due to visual distrust. The platform needed differentiation in a crowded education market.</p></div></section>
  <section class="project-section-alt"><div class="container"><span class="section-label-text"><i>02</i> System</span><p class="project-body">Complete identity system with a color palette balancing authority and approachability. Improved information hierarchy for courses. Professional visual presence reflecting content quality.</p></div></section>
  <section class="project-gallery"><div class="container"><div class="project-colors"><div class="row" style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;">{[{bg:'#0C395A',c:'white'},{bg:'#1975C2',c:'white'},{bg:'#54A3FF',c:'white'},{bg:'#C1E2FF',c:'black'},{bg:'#10232A',c:'white'},{bg:'#1E3740',c:'white'},{bg:'#2B4A56',c:'white'},{bg:'#EEF7FB',c:'black'},{bg:'#2B8842',c:'white'},{bg:'#53FF71',c:'black'}].map(c => <div class="ColorSample p-3" style={`background:${c.bg};min-width:120px;flex:1`}><p style={`color:${c.c};margin:0;font-family:monospace;font-size:0.8rem`}>{c.bg}</p></div>)}</div></div></div></section>
  <section class="project-result"><div class="container"><div class="result-box"><h2>Result</h2><p>Brand perception improvement. Scalable color system for new courses. Estimated reduction in course page drop-off due to visual clarity.</p></div></div></section>
</BaseLayout>